                            <comment id="14259647" author="tilman" created="Sun, 28 Dec 2014 14:10:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m currently working on this, and this will be done in two steps:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;apply inverted ctm and xform to each coordinate in getRaster, as I already do with type1 shading (works fine, see attachment) but without the optimizations&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;reintroduce the optimizations in the new code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Other files with the same problem:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2344&quot; title=&quot;NegativeArraySizeException in radial shading&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2344&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2344&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-233644-p10.pdf (axial, see &quot;rolling&quot; and &quot;scrap processing&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;PATTYP1.pdf (axial, the &quot;L&quot; shadings must be diagonal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14259710" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 28 Dec 2014 19:50:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1648248 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1648248&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1648248&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2217&quot; title=&quot;Matrix transform ignored in axial and radial shadings (in PDFToImage output)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2217&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2217&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: apply transforms in getRaster instead of construction to be able to render shadings with different x and y transforms&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14259731" author="tilman" created="Sun, 28 Dec 2014 21:52:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lmpmbernardo&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lmpmbernardo&quot;&gt;lmpmbernardo&lt;/a&gt; thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14260104" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 29 Dec 2014 13:37:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1648336 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1648336&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1648336&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2217&quot; title=&quot;Matrix transform ignored in axial and radial shadings (in PDFToImage output)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2217&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2217&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: remove factor min value, as it doesn&apos;t make much visual difference&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265041" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 5 Jan 2015 20:19:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1649638 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649638&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1649638&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2217&quot; title=&quot;Matrix transform ignored in axial and radial shadings (in PDFToImage output)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2217&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2217&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: use transform() because getScaleX() doesn&apos;t work properly with a 90&#176; rotated matrix&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265052" author="tilman" created="Mon, 5 Jan 2015 20:24:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached file was all blue without gradient before the latest change. It has a 90&#176; rotation, so there is an AffineTransform that has 0 &quot;scale&quot; elements. See also near the end of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1094&quot; title=&quot;Pattern colorspace support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1094&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1094&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for a discussion about that problem and why &quot;scale&quot; elements do not always represent the scale.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14265055" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 5 Jan 2015 20:29:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1649649 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1649649&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1649649&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2217&quot; title=&quot;Matrix transform ignored in axial and radial shadings (in PDFToImage output)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2217&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2217&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: forgot comment&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
